{"tid":1854611,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳馮富珍：中國在處理疫情方面的表現　全球都「點讚」","createTime":"2020-01-31T14:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T02:44:30.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":394,"uniUserReply":127,"replies":[{"pid":"d0641a7aa417ba37a7487c69e645026431c08c6c","tid":1854611,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"世界衞生組織(WHO)將新型冠狀病毒疫情，列為「國際關注的突發公共衞生事件」。世衞前總幹事陳馮富珍認為，這並非針對中國，更不是對中國處理疫情方面的不信任，稱對中國的表現，全球都「點讚」。<br />\n<br />\n陳馮富珍接受新華社專訪時指出，世衞的決定是科學的判斷，很謹慎很合理的決定，目的是為了更好地控制疫情，不讓疫情在全球散播。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，新型冠狀病毒是新病毒，很難估算疫情何時減退，目前還有很多不清楚的地方，要待專家繼續加緊研究。當務之急是落實中央政府的一系列措施，包括早發現、早報告、早隔離、早治療，做好聯防聯控的工作。只要做好上述措施，有信心國家能夠戰勝疫情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2366101/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2366101%2F&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=6ce2bc72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2366101/</a>"},{"pid":"973b8c6c33b794c1541baac5d1d039d89c77cae9","tid":1854611,"uid":49336,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nusoOoa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnusoOoa.jpg&h=d5f12261&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a2fe4804663bd79f6f241648d687a9c09ad7926","tid":1854611,"uid":12628,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:45:10.000Z","msg":"比人ban晒=點讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5333c51e6bf6201a70e3e3a00b17f5db6c533ac1","tid":1854611,"uid":74171,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:45:42.000Z","msg":"點可以讚？<br />\n咁on9 都講得出？"},{"pid":"839af5668f6367e49f124d96fcf86a846bbb2973","tid":1854611,"uid":55162,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:46:18.000Z","msg":"比人禁入境係讚你處理疫情做得好<br />\n精神勝利法真係唔夠終國人嚟"},{"pid":"7